# Web Finance Control Center

Web is not only a viewer.

Required modules:
- Dashboard
- Project
- Saldo Project
- Transaction
- Approval Center
- Reconciliation
- Settlement PIC
- Transfer
- Budget
- Reports
- Sync Monitor
- Audit Trail
- User Management
- Device Management
- Project Assignment

Approved transaction cannot be edited directly.
Use correction or void.
Dangerous actions require reason, confirmation, permission, and audit log.
